quran[18{c,v,t}:
52,32,kya inn ki aqlain iِnhain aisi hi baatein karne ke liye kehti hain? ya Dur haqeeqat yeh inaad mein hadd se guzray hue log hain ?
52,33,kya yeh kehte hain ke iss shakhs ne yeh quran khud ghurr liya hai? asal baat yeh hai ke yeh imaan nahi lana chahtay
52,34,agar yeh apne iss qoul mein sachey hain to aِsi shaan ka aik kalaam bana layein
52,35,kya yeh kisi khaaliq ke baghair khud peda ho gay hain? ya yeh khud apne khaaliq hain ?
52,36,ya zameen aur asmano ko unhon ne peda kya hai? asal baat yeh hai ke yeh yaqeen nahi rakhtay
52,37,kya tairay rab ke khazanay inn ke qabzay mein hain? ya unn par aِnhi ka hukum chalta hai ?
52,38,kya inn ke paas koi seerhi hai jis par charh kar yeh aalam baala ki sun gun letay hain? inn mein se jis ne sun gun li ho woh laaye koi khuli Daleel
52,39,kya Allah ke liye to hain betiyan aur tum logon ke liye hain betay ?
52,40,kya tum inn se koi ajar mangte ho ke yeh zabardasti pari hui chti ke boojh taley dabey jatay hain ?
52,41,kya inn ke paas ghaib ke haqayiq ka ilm hai ke uss ki bana par yeh likh rahay hon ?
52,42,kya yeh koi chaal chalna chahtay hain? ( agar yeh baat hai ) to kufar karne walon par un ki chaal ulti hi parre gi
52,43,kya Allah ke siwa yeh koi aur mabood rakhtay hain? Allah pak hai uss shirk se jo yeh log kar rahay hain
52,44,yeh log aasman ke tukre bhi girtay hue dekh len to kahin ge yeh baadal hain jo amde chalay aa rahay hain
52,45,"pas ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, aِnhin inn ke haal par chore do yahan taq ke yeh apne uss din ko poanch jayen jis mein yeh maar giraye jayen ge"
52,46,jis din nah inn ki apni koi chaal inn ke kisi kaam aeye gi nah koi inn ki madad ko aeye ga
52,47,"aur uss waqt ke anay se pehlay bhi zaalmon ke liye aik azaab hai, magar inn mein se aksar jantay nahi hain"
52,48,"ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, apne rab ka faisla anay taq sabr karo, tum hamari nigah mein ho tum jab utho to apne rab ki hamd ke sath is ki tasbeeh karo"
52,49,raat ko bhi is ki tasbeeh kya karo aur setaaray jab palatne hain uss waqt bhi
